{"id":275565,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-山东临沂维权人士刘国慧被软禁家中（图/","date":"2013-01-21T15:30:52Z","modified":"2013-01-21T15:30:52Z","title":"维权网 | 山东临沂维权人士刘国慧被软禁家中（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员赵醒民、雷鸣报道）本网信息员获悉，山东临沂维权维权人士刘国慧因到北京上访被押回临沂后，遭到当地政法委指示居委会十多人的看守，目前一切外出都须经看守同意，并坐看守的车，每天吃饭也由看守购买送入。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘国慧因为遭遇强拆，多年来不断上访上诉，均无法得到解决。本月她与临沂另外五名拆迁受害人前往北京，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>号到中国戏剧学院向彭丽缓山东老乡陈情，在学院门口遭到山东驻京办人员拦截，并被驻京办人员雇佣黑社会成员殴打，押回临沂后，这些上访人分别受到提自所在区街道办或居委会的看守。刘国慧被当地政法部门认为是这次上访的组织者，而遭到更为严密的软禁。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据悉，在刘国慧居住的房屋后边小院中有专门监控刘国慧的办公室，不仅摄像头二十四小时监视，大门口两辆警车也二十四小时值守。十几个人轮流值班，不许外面任何人与刘国慧接触。就是吃饭都得由看守购买送入。刘国慧所用的手机也被屏蔽，外面上访的人也无法联系到她。如此严密看守，显然借用了当年看守陈光诚的经验。另外，看守明确告诉刘国慧春节前不可能对她放松监控。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>以下图片是刘国慧家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年元月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日的情况</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、停在刘国慧家门前的监控车辆</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、安装在刘国慧后院邻居家监控她家大门口区域的摄像头</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、刘国慧家门口的监控人员</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>、停在刘国慧后院邻居家门前的监控车辆（监控人员平常都躲在二楼监控室）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-K-EcCtdYzBs/UPzDm6PfcyI/AAAAAAAAZq4/g8UE34Y8-HA/s1600/1%E3%80%81%E5%81%9C%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E6%85%A7%E5%AE%B6%E9%97%A8%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E8%BD%A6%E8%BE%86.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-K-EcCtdYzBs/UPzDm6PfcyI/AAAAAAAAZq4/g8UE34Y8-HA/s320/1%E3%80%81%E5%81%9C%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E6%85%A7%E5%AE%B6%E9%97%A8%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E8%BD%A6%E8%BE%86.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-dSQPa6ojHiA/UPzDn_8irwI/AAAAAAAAZrA/1N86KgardmQ/s1600/5%E3%80%81%E5%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E6%85%A7%E5%AE%B6%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-dSQPa6ojHiA/UPzDn_8irwI/AAAAAAAAZrA/1N86KgardmQ/s320/5%E3%80%81%E5%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E6%85%A7%E5%AE%B6%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%A3%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3YPnq46aqhI/UPzDoiALf1I/AAAAAAAAZrE/E5itB-9St_U/s1600/6%E3%80%81%E5%81%9C%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E6%85%A7%E5%90%8E%E9%99%A2%E9%82%BB%E5%B1%85%E5%AE%B6%E9%97%A8%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E8%BD%A6%E8%BE%86.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3YPnq46aqhI/UPzDoiALf1I/AAAAAAAAZrE/E5itB-9St_U/s320/6%E3%80%81%E5%81%9C%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E6%85%A7%E5%90%8E%E9%99%A2%E9%82%BB%E5%B1%85%E5%AE%B6%E9%97%A8%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E8%BD%A6%E8%BE%86.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vq999NtaxSI/UPzDo8NQV5I/AAAAAAAAZrI/TE_3qCDblk8/s1600/4%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E6%85%A7%E5%90%8E%E9%99%A2%E9%82%BB%E5%B1%85%E5%AE%B6%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E5%A5%B9%E5%AE%B6%E5%A4%A7%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%A3%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%91%84%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%B4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vq999NtaxSI/UPzDo8NQV5I/AAAAAAAAZrI/TE_3qCDblk8/s320/4%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%9C%A8%E5%88%98%E5%9B%BD%E6%85%A7%E5%90%8E%E9%99%A2%E9%82%BB%E5%B1%85%E5%AE%B6%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E5%A5%B9%E5%AE%B6%E5%A4%A7%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%A3%E5%8C%BA%E5%9F%9F%E7%9A%84%E6%91%84%E5%83%8F%E5%A4%B4.jpg\" width=\"320\"